How were things at Gaia?

94
00:04:27,612 --> 00:04:28,842
What are you doing here?

95
00:04:28,922 --> 00:04:31,152
She saw the TV show this morning
and got worried,

96
00:04:31,152 --> 00:04:32,452
so she rushed over here.

97
00:04:32,922 --> 00:04:33,892
What a girl.

98
00:04:34,052 --> 00:04:37,252
