in this hotel?

100
00:04:40,432 --> 00:04:42,452
Shin emailed me to let me know.

101
00:04:42,602 --> 00:04:44,222
How thoughtful of you.

102
00:04:44,632 --> 00:04:46,502
I knew she would come.

103
00:04:46,972 --> 00:04:49,232
Misato says she'll be
staying here for a while.

104
00:04:49,642 --> 00:04:51,712
She can run errands for us,

105
