Overcoming adversities is her pride.

163
00:07:39,312 --> 00:07:41,272
But I have my pride too.

164
00:07:42,012 --> 00:07:44,742
In the end, Gaia could care less
about our sound.

165
00:07:45,512 --> 00:07:47,782
Is this what a big record label
should be doing?

166
00:07:48,852 --> 00:07:51,822
You know, that's how all
big companies operate.

167
00:07:52,152 --> 00:07:53,792
If it sells, anything goes.

168
00:07:53,792 --> 00:07:54,692
Yasu!

169
00:07:54,692 --> 00:07:58,852
