that Gaia is tied up to.

174
00:08:16,242 --> 00:08:19,182
So, you see, they have to get along
with each other

175
00:08:19,182 --> 00:08:20,582
to maintain their present relationship.

176
00:08:22,252 --> 00:08:25,652
