prevail in this world.

198
00:09:47,402 --> 00:09:49,872
If you don't wanna lose,
you've gotta be tough.

199
00:09:51,812 --> 00:09:53,772
You've gotta be more cunning.

200
00:10:02,682 --> 00:10:06,172
