he is aiming for.

207
00:10:41,052 --> 00:10:47,492
I remembered us talking about
living together in that warehouse again,

208
00:10:47,492 --> 00:10:50,602
and began to think that it was
even less likely to come true

209
00:10:50,602 --> 00:10:54,122
than my dream of making it
as a singer.

210
00:10:59,742 --> 00:11:03,332
