and then flees off to school.

216
00:11:16,122 --> 00:11:17,962
Men can be so selfish.

217
00:11:17,962 --> 00:11:20,392
When's he coming back?
We haven't made up yet after that fight.

218
00:11:20,392 --> 00:11:21,022
