HACHIKO
Nana's hanging in there,

225
00:11:35,312 --> 00:11:37,112
HACHIKO
no matter how tough things
are for her,

226
00:11:37,112 --> 00:11:38,812
HACHIKO
so I've gotta gather myself
and do my best too.

227
